thread.title: Sharon's Garden

author: Sharon's Garden
title: Sharon's Garden
text: I was looking for a certain type of tree one that could be used for medicinal purposes and that can grow in my zone. I found my trees, placed my order and they were here quite quickly. They were very well packaged and bigger that I thought they would be. I will be glad once they mature out. I highly recommend Willis Orchard and will be ordering more in the future.
